{"tid":1181414,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"單身太久了…","createTime":"2019-06-01T15:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T15:39:14.000Z","uid":76885,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7076734f45ca8d7d622b8fe32345dadd90aa06f1","tid":1181414,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwhXZLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwhXZLV.jpg&h=6f9121eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪大部份男人都會咁？<br />\n即係&hellip;好易覺得人吸引？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女人呢？<br />\n單身耐，係咪都好易覺得人吸引？<br />\n<br />\n好奇呢種狀態，係咪好多人類都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a7d01a96a2a980bd4f37110b470af7441529c2","tid":1181414,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"見到女仔冇乜反應<br />\n反而見到男仔會扯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093fb87a9be105bc8a9488b54de246d63633a795","tid":1181414,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2741683b13ef20c15ea11ad109179c6e960ada2","tid":1181414,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c9d10b4c5938b063d643e562fdcb3fbecc4251","tid":1181414,"uid":76885,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"093fb87a9be105bc8a9488b54de246d63633a795","tid":1181414,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n我自己立場好似一路都無咩變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係：<br />\n<br />\n世界有好多吸引既人。<br />\n吸引唔等如適合。<br />\n同唔適合既人一齊，痛苦過自己一個人。<br />\n<br />\n所以自己唔會特別叫春。<br />\n又唔特別想拍拖。<br />\n又知自己唔吸引所以無特別大希望。<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n但&hellip;<br />\n又就真係好容易覺遇到既人吸引。<br />\n<br />\n開頭覺得&hellip;<br />\n係咪自己要求低？<br />\n係咪自己喺任何人身上都容易搵到好既野吸引既野？<br />\n<br />\n然後最近越嚟越感覺到&hellip;<br />\n種感覺似係身體或欲望既反應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n不過依然覺得&hellip;<br />\n唔適合唔適合&hellip;<br />\n腦袋都係一路講唔適合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過可能唔係對方唔適合自己？<br />\n更多係&hellip;自己唔適合對方？<br />\n<br />\n4<br />\nLoop loop loop。<br />\n好意識到全部steps既內心小電影。<br />\n<br />\n但又好奇&hellip;<br />\n其他人呢？<br />\n個經驗係點？<br />\n心入面&hellip;有無&hellip;或者有啲咩內心戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361c461a2e1abb421d950a7e3ddd6c2c87b9430e","tid":1181414,"uid":225247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"樓主有乜好怕<br />\n我由出世到宜家都單身"},{"pid":"bebe3885af323c26ab1b04406c290572453c2547","tid":1181414,"uid":76885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2741683b13ef20c15ea11ad109179c6e960ada2","tid":1181414,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3801f08c4458a9d16a9b8e5a73c49270a9c4dd30","tid":1181414,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:27:48.000Z","msg":"習慣左又有咩好怕喎<br />\n人又唔係一開始就一對對"},{"pid":"99127292f9ba9517653114378e3a82cec7a19b12","tid":1181414,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"361c461a2e1abb421d950a7e3ddd6c2c87b9430e","tid":1181414,"uid":2